        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Employer Participation in Student Loan Assistance Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to extend the tax exclusion for employer-provided educational assistance to include payments of qualified education loans paid to either an employee or a lender.</p>]]></text>
